'''2-异氰基丙烷'''是一种[[有机化合物|有机化合物]]，化学式为[[C4H7N|C<sub>4</sub>H<sub>7</sub>N]]，它是[[异丁腈|异丁腈]]的[[同分异构体|同分异构体]]。它可由[[异丙胺|异丙胺]]和[[三氯甲烷|三氯甲烷]]在[[氢氧化钠|氢氧化钠]]和[[季铵盐|季铵盐]]的存在下在溶剂中反应得到<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Bioorganic & Medicinal Chemistry Letters|volume=26|issue=7|language=en|date=2016-04|pages=1762–1766|doi=10.1016/j.bmcl.2016.02.039|url=https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S0960894X16301524|title=Synthesis and structure–activity relationship of α-keto amides as enterovirus 71 3C protease inhibitors|accessdate=2021-04-07|author=Debin Zeng, Yuying Ma, Rui Zhang, Quandeng Nie, Zhengjie Cui, Yaxin Wang, Luqing Shang, Zheng Yin|archive-date=2018-06-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180623171702/https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S0960894X16301524}}</ref>，''N''-异丙基甲酰胺和[[三氯氧磷|三氯氧磷]]在[[三乙胺|三乙胺]]的存在下于[[二氯甲烷|二氯甲烷]]中反应，也可得到2-异氰基丙烷。<ref name=Wang>{{cite journal|journal=Organic & Biomolecular Chemistry|volume=13|issue=47|language=en|issn=1477-0520|date=2015|pages=11486–11491|doi=10.1039/C5OB01659B|url=http://xlink.rsc.org/?DOI=C5OB01659B|title=Palladium-catalyzed direct coupling of 2-vinylanilines and isocyanides: an efficient synthesis of 2-aminoquinolines|accessdate=2021-04-07|author=Lijie Wang, Jamie Ferguson, Fanlong Zeng}}</ref>它可作为配体和金属形成[[配合物|配合物]]。<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Chemistry - A European Journal|volume=23|issue=56|language=en|date=2017-10-09|pages=14027–14038|doi=10.1002/chem.201702998|url=http://doi.wiley.com/10.1002/chem.201702998|title=C−C and C−N Couplings Following Hydride Addition on Isocyanide Cyclopolyenyl Dimolybdenum Complexes to Give Tethered Aldimine and Aminocarbene Derivatives|accessdate=2021-04-07|author=Belén Alvarez, M. Angeles Alvarez, M. Esther García, Daniel García-Vivó, Miguel A. Ruiz}}</ref>

